5 Section 5. There is hereby appropriated General Fund moneys in the amount of
6 $30,000,000 in each fiscal year of the 2026-2028 fiscal biennium to the Kentucky Public
7 Transportation Development Fund established under Section 1 of this Act.
8 Section 6. Whereas public transportation provides environmental, economic,
9 and social equity domain benefits for communities in the Commonwealth, an emergency
10 is declared to exist, and this Act takes effect upon its passage and approval by the
11 Governor or upon its otherwise becoming a law.
